---
title: Gnocchi in Beef and Pork Ragu with Spinach and Parmesan
description: This meaty ragu blends juicy beef and pork for a delicious switch from your typical all beef sauce. Hearty gnocchi brings texture to every bite, and it's all finished off with cheese for good measure!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/gnocchis-a-la-sauce-ragu-au-boeuf-et-au-porc-234195c8.jpg
